               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> <gramGrp> <pos expand="Substantivum">subst.</pos> </gramGrp> [arab. <foreign xml:lang="ar">مَنْدِيلٌ مِنْدِيلٌ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> mantile; </quote></cit> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> linteum, quo mulieres caput cingunt </quote></cit>] <lbl expand="pluralis">Pl.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">መንዲላት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Sx. Genb." loc="21">Sx. Genb. 21</ref>; <sense n="1" xml:id="D1"> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> mantile </quote></cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክርስቶስ፡ ቀነተ፡ መንዲለ፡ ወኀፀበ፡ እግረ፡ አርዳኢሁ፡</foreign> M.M. f. 195 <ref target="#c1428"/>. <cb n="0195" xml:id="c0195"/> 
</sense> <sense n="2" xml:id="D2"> nomen vestimenti sacerdotalis, ut videtur: <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἐπιτραχήλιον</foreign> seu <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> stola </quote></cit> collo circumposita et in crucis formam circa humeros decussata (<lbl expand="videas">vid.</lbl> Renaudot liturg. I. p. 179; Renaudot liturg. I. p. 180): <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለትኩን፡ ልብስ፡ ዘትወርድ፡ እስከ፡ አእጋረ፡ ካህናት፡ ወዓዲ፡ ትኩን፡ ላዕለ፡ መታክፍቲሆሙ፡ መንዲል፡ ስፍሕት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="F.N." loc=" 12">F.N.  12</ref>; accuratiora de vestimentis sacerdotum praecepta haec sunt: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወይኩኑ፡ ለለመታክፍቲሆሙ፡ ዝናራት፡ ዘውእቶሙ፡ ፊቃር፡ ወኢይኩኑ፡ ረቂቃተ። እምትእዛዘ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ዘ፷ ለይኩን፡ አልባሰ፡ ክህነቱ፡ ለካህን፡ ካልእ፡ እምአልባሰ፡ ሕዝባውያን። ይደሉ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩን፡ ቀሚስ፡ ስፉየ፡ ወዕውደ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ጀይብ፡</foreign> (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘይመስል፡ ከመ፡ ኽረጺት፡</foreign>)<foreign xml:lang="gez">። ወጠሊሳኑኒ፡ ይኩን፡ ጽዕድወ፤ አክሊሉኒ፡ ክሉለ፡ መልዕልተ፡ ርእሱ፡ ወይኩን፡ ዘውረ፡ አክሊሉ፡ ስፉሐ፡ ወስፉየ፡ በሠላስ፡ መዓርጋተ፡ ስፍየት። ወከመዝ፡ ካዕበ፡ መዛርዐ፡ ቀሚሱኒ፡ ይኩኑ፡ ዕውዳነ፡ እስመ፡ ዝንቱ፡ አምሳለ፡ ማእሰሩ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ በሐብል፡ ወኩትፈተ፡ እደዊሁ፡ ፪ቱ። ወካዕበ፡ ይልበስ፡ ካህን፡ መንዲለ፡ ዘቦቱ፡ ትእምርተ፡ መስቀል፡ ዘወረዱ፡</foreign> (<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> cujus latitudo </quote></cit>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">የሐጽጽ፡ ወይንእስ፡ ንስቲተ፡ እምጠሊሳን፡ ወይግበር፡ ምስቁለ፡ ላዕለ፡ መታክፍቲሁ፡ ፪ እስመ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ይትሜሰል፡ ካዕበ፡ በአርአያ፡ ሐብል፡ ዘወደዩ፡ አይሁድ፡ ዲበ፡ ክሣደ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="F.M." loc=" 31,5">F.M.  31,5</ref>; archangelus <foreign xml:lang="gez">ገብርኤል፡ ዘጸዳለ፡ ብርሃን፡ መንዲሉ፡</foreign> I <ref cRef="Sal. Mar." loc="15.">Sal. Mar. 15.</ref> 
</sense> <sense n="3" xml:id="D3"> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> fascia, quae capiti circumvolvitur </quote></cit>, Lud. e Mss. Colb.
</sense> <sense n="4" xml:id="D4"> in lingua amh. <foreign xml:lang="gez">መንዲል፡</foreign> significat <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> sudarium </quote></cit> (teste Isenbergio).
</sense> </sense>
               
